Kamfanin ya zama kamar Goop na Gwyneth Paltrou kuma ya ninka dukiyar da ake kira £11m.
Bayan da 'yar shekara 37 mai suna Willowbi ta wallafa a shafinta na Instagram cewa za ta bar Truly, Jones ya yi tafiya a wasu gidajensa a waje da Birtaniya.
