'Yan sanda suna fafatawa da 'yan ta'adda na Catalonia a ranar da aka yi wa 'yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan rikici tsakanin masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai da jami'an gyara tsarin mulki, yayin da dubban mutane ke halartar zanga-zangar bikin cika shekaru biyu da zaɓe na raba ƙasar Catalonia wanda ya haifar da rikici.
Wasu masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai da suka yi amfani da masks da aka tsare da su da kuma 'yan sanda sun jefa ƙwai da fenti a cikin turmi, suna samar da girgije mai duhu a kan tituna da yawanci masu yawon bude ido ke cika su.
A wani lokaci kuma, an yi rikici a rana da 'yan sanda suna amfani da makamai don su danne rikici.
Don sa'o'i da yawa, ƙungiyoyin masu goyon bayan 'yancin kai na Catalonia sun yi ihu da taken "Ba mu gafarta ba, ba mu manta ba" ga ƙungiyoyin masu zanga-zangar haɗin kai na ƙasar suna ihu "Bari Spain ta rayu".
Mutane 14 ne aka kwantar da su asibiti da ƙananan raunuka da suka faru a lokacin zanga-zangar, in ji jaridar yankin.
Tashin hankali ya ci gaba da kasancewa a yankin da ke goyon bayan 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan an yi watsi da zaben 1 ga Oktoba a Madrid, wanda masu mulkin mallaka na Catalonia ke yi.
