Wannan begen ya yi ƙarfi a yau fiye da kowane lokaci a cikin shekaru da yawa, yayin da Bolivia ke jiran hukuncin Kotun Duniya a ranar 1 ga Oktoba bayan shekaru biyar na shawarwari.
"Bolivia tana da ƙarfi, tana da ruhun haɗin kai da kwanciyar hankali, kuma tana sa ido ga sakamakon da kyau", in ji Roberto Calzandala, wani diflomasiyyar Bolivia.
