Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara taron jama'a da ke farawa a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne taro na farko daga cikin taro biyar da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya ƙunshi yawon bude ido zuwa yankunan da ke kusa da su kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da za a yi zaben tabbatar da zabarsa na Kotun Koli a jiran lokaci, Trump na neman karfafa goyon bayan jama'a ga zaben na wucin gadi da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke cikin haɗarin rasa iko da majalisa ta hanyar zaben na Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia a yau, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon taron a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia an shirya shi ne don karfe 7 na dare ET, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a cikin YouTube.
Trump na iya yin magana a cikin sauraron wannan makon game da dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya faru a cikin yanayi mai rikitarwa saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i, tare da amincewar Majalisar Dattawa da aka dakatar da shi har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Duk da haka, babban burin wannan taron shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar sakamakon rashin daidaituwa a zaben Nuwamba don samun wani ƙarfi.
A cewar Reuters, ofishin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce, waɗannan taro biyar na mako mai zuwa suna nufin "shirya hankalin masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da faɗaɗa rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Dattijai".
"Sarrafawa da majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga tsarinsa, wanda shugaban ya yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda ya yiwu, yayin da muke tafiya cikin lokacin da yaƙin neman zaɓe ya kasance mai wahala", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya gaya wa Reuters, wanda ya so ya kasance ba a san shi ba.
Taron da aka shirya a yammacin yau a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata, jihar da ta ci nasara da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican a West Virginia don majalisar dattijai, wanda ke da ƙananan kuri'u.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba shi turawa zuwa zaben", in ji Simon Hunter, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
