'Yan wasan da suka fi Spitth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin Ryder Cup.
Ƙananan 'yan'uwa maza biyu da ke Turai sun yi nasara a matsayi na hudu a cikin hudu kuma ba su da wata matsala.
"Mollywood" ita ce kawai tagwayen da ba ta buga bogey a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma ta kuma guji bogey a ranar Asabar da safe, da yammacin Juma'a da kuma baya tara a ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wannan wasan, da kuma yadda makamashi ke gudana a tsakanin masu sauraro masu sautin baki, ya nuna cewa 'yan wasan ne za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi kuma babu wani dan wasan da ya fi farin ciki fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari don ya yi nasara a Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau a yi su biyu a lokaci guda a rami daban-daban.
Wannan shi ne dalilin da ya sa ake bukatar mu yi magana game da ɗaukakar Turai.
Babba Watson da Webb Simpson sun saka tabarau a kan Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan kwallon kafa na safe, lokacin da yake wasa da Alex Noren.
Da bogey guda biyu da kuma ninki biyu a gaba tara sun jefa Mutanen Espanya da Swede cikin rami sosai har ba su iya fita daga ciki ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga rami.
Fourball da foursome wasanni ne masu ban sha'awa don kallon su a hankali saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, da shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, da shawarwarin da ba sa bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun zai iya canzawa a cikin lokaci.
Turai ta yi fice a matsayin tawagar har zuwa yanzu kuma tana da gagarumin ci gaba a ranar ƙarshe, amma wannan gwagwarmayar ta nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da ƙarfin hali, duk da shakku na wasu.
Turai ta samu ci gaba 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta samu nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder bayan ta ci gaba da buga wasan hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ta yi 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Ƙwararrun 'yan wasan biyu na Tommy Fleetwood da Francisco Molinari sun yi nasara biyu a kan mai tsaron Tiger Woods kuma sun samu nasarar samun ci gaba a Le Golf National har zuwa yanzu a maki hudu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Björn, wadda ke ƙoƙarin riƙe kofin da ta yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka shige, ta ci gaba da rinjayar ƙwararrun 'yan Amirka a wasan da suka yi a safiyar yau, ta ci 3-1.
Amurka ta yi tsayayya da mafi yawan 'yan hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rufe bambanci ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga cikin wasanni 12 na ranar Lahadi don ya ci gaba da cin kofin.
Flightwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya fara fitowa wanda ya ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da tare da Molinari, wanda aka fi sani da "Mollywood", bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki shine kawai ma'aurata na biyu da suka ci maki hudu a farkon wasanni huɗu a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan foorball, sun haɗa kai don su ci nasara a kan wani gajiyar Woods da kuma sabon Amurkawa Bryson DeSabo da wani 5&4 mai ban mamaki.
Woods, wanda ya yi tsalle a wasannin biyu na Asabar, ya nuna fashewar haske na yau da kullum, amma ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasannin 29 a cikin huduball da foursome da kuma jerin bakwai.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta don wasan hudu na safe, ya koma ga abokin aikin Henryk Stenson don wasan hudu tare da 2&1 da aka yi wa Dustin Johnson da Brooks Keppka, yana samun matsayi na farko da na uku a duniya.
Ba kome ba ne da ya yi kyau ga Turai, duk da rana mai sanyi da farin ciki a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Wasan da ya lashe gasar sau uku, Jordan Spitth da kuma Justin Thomas sun yi nasara a gasar da aka yi a ranar Asabar.
Sun samu nasara mai wuya 2&1 a kan John Ram da Ian Poulter na Spain a cikin foursball kuma sun dawo daga baya don cin nasarar Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a foursome yayin da suka rasa ramukan biyu a buɗe.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup wani rukuni ya samu nasara yayin da ya rasa maki hudu a cikin na'urar guda, ko da yake saboda shi ne mai cin nasara, Furik ya isa ya yi wasan da ya dace don riƙe trophy.
Amma, tun da yake ya kasance a matsayi na biyu na kwanaki biyu, ya bayyana cewa, yaƙi da su a ranar Lahadi ba zai yiwu ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta yi watsi da makamai ba tare da amincewa da matakan da ake ɗauka ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumin yana kara kara jin rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma kasarsa ba za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya ba a irin wannan yanayin.
A taron koli na shekara-shekara na kungiyar, Ri Yong Ho ya bayyana cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "babban matakan kirki" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na kwando, lalata wuraren gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma alkawarin hana yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan amsa daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a amince da tsaronmu na kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayin babu wata hanyar da za mu fara kawar da makamanmu".
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafin Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya ta Washington game da yiwuwar "taƙaice" tsarin kawar da makaman nukiliya, wanda zai ba da lada ga Koriya ta Arewa yayin da ta ci gaba da aiwatar da shi, sanarwa ta kasance mai mahimmanci a cikin cewa bai ƙyale kawar da makaman nukiliya gaba ɗaya ba, kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da sanarwar da Kim Jong-un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko da aka yi tsakanin wani shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "yankin nukiliya na yankin Koriya", yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbacin tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa tana neman ta kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara "ba da" makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma yi tsayayya da kiran da ake yi na sassauta tsauraran takunkumin kasa da kasa da aka sanya wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace a yi watsi da makaman nukiliya da farko kuma tana kara matsa lamba ta hanyar barazanar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar zalunta, ta hanyar hana ko da nuna ƙarshen yaƙi", in ji Ri.
"Sanar da cewa za a iya yin hukunci a kan gwiwoyinmu mafarki ne ga waɗanda ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da tsaurara takunkumi yana ƙara ɓata mana amana".
Ri bai yi wani rahoto ba game da shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump, wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana da shi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Sai dai ya yi nuni da ganawar da Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in suka yi a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kuma kara da cewa: "Idan da Koriya ta Kudu ce ta kasance abokin tarayya a batun kawar da makaman nukiliya maimakon Amurka, kawar da makaman nukiliya daga yankin Koriya ba za ta kai ga irin wannan rashin tsaro ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Re's ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya ce a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa harin Amurka da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa ba makawa ne saboda "Shugaba" Trump ya kira Kim "mai linzami" a aikin kashe kansa.
A Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a wannan shekara, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "dakatar da" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim don ƙarfin hali na ci gaba da matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce akwai sauran abubuwa da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a ci gaba da tsaurara tanadi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da jadawalin yin hakan, yana cewa, "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku, ko watanni biyar, ba kome".
Kasar Sin da Rasha sun ce Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci Pyongyang ta biya shi lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Tallafin da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta yi na tsaurara da kuma ci gaba da kai tsaye har sai an cimma cikakken, karshe da kuma tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Majalisar tsaron ta amince da takunkumi a kan Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 a kokarin hana samun kudade don shirin nukiliya da makaman nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a kan iyakokin babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ba ya tafiya sosai.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, sai Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi sa'o'i kadan bayan haka cewa yana da "bukatun gangster".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a wani taro da Moon a wannan watan ta yi watsi da wani makami mai linzami da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakai masu dacewa".
Ya bayyana cewa Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema sune tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi wa Singapore alkawari kuma suna inganta daidaitaccen dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyar da yadda za su sami isasshen hutu
A wannan shekara, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard ya bukaci dukan daliban digiri na biyu su yi barci sosai a ƙoƙarin magance yawan yawan al'adun daren da ke tattare da yawan shan maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗaliban jami'a na farko a duniya ba su san ainihin abubuwa ba, kamar yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Chysler, Farfesa a Harvard Medical School kuma likita ne a asibitin Brigham and Women's, ya tsara wannan darasin, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare ta ta soma darasi bayan ta yi jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan koyo.
"A ƙarshe, wata yarinya ta zo ta ce mini, 'Me ya sa nake koyo game da wannan yanzu, a cikin shekarar ƙarshe na?'
Ta ce ba a taɓa gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci ba - abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji ta a cikin jaridar The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa dalibai muhimman ka'idoji game da yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa wajen samun nasara a ilimi da kuma wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyar jama'a.
Paul Barrera, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma darektan kula da lafiyar jami'a, ya ce jami'a ta yanke shawarar hada da wannan darasin lokacin da aka gano cewa ɗalibai suna fama da rashin barci a cikin mako.
A darasi na sa'a ɗaya, za a yi aiki mai ma'ana.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana na dalibai, inda ɗalibai ke danna kan kofuna na kofi, labule, takalma na wasanni, da littattafai, don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki, da kuma muhimmancin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, masu halartar taron sun koyi yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon zuciya, ciwon zuciya, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke nuna hotuna masu ma'ana ta ƙarfafa masu halartar taron su yi tunani a kan rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba zai canja halin ɗalibai ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin sanin, kamar yadda kuke da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan taba sigari a kan lafiyarku", in ji Farfesa Chiseller.
Ya ce, al'adar yin alfahari da yin nazari dukan dare tana nan har yanzu, kuma ya ƙara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma matsi da ake yi a kan ɗalibai yana nufin cewa rashin barci matsala ce da ke ci gaba da ƙaruwa.
Ya ce, samun isasshen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na ɗalibai don magance damuwa, gajiya, da kuma damuwa, har ma don kauce wa yin nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta yi yunwa, wanda ke haifar da jin yunwa na kullum.
Raymond Shaw, ɗan shekara 19 daga California da ke nazarin ilmin sunadarai da ilimin halitta, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Chiseller wajen tsara darasin, bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin azuzuwansa na ƙarshe a shekara ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce darasin ya sa ya soma tunani sosai kuma ya sa ya yi wa'azi a dukan harabar.
Ta yi fatan za a bukaci dukan daliban digiri na biyu su halarci irin wannan shirin kafin su fara karatu a wannan makarantar da ke da matukar gasa.
Farfesa Chysler ya shawarci ɗalibai su saita sanarwar lokacin da za su yi barci, da kuma farkawa don lokacin farkawa, kuma su san haɗarin "hasken blue" da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke haifarwa, wanda zai iya ɓata yanayin motsa jiki, yana haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston - Rangers 1-0: Mengha ya ci wa Gerard 'yan wasan kwallo
'Yan wasan Rangers sun sha wahala a wani mummunan rashin nasara a waje, kamar yadda bugun Dolly Menga ya jagoranci ɓacin rai na Steven Gerrard zuwa 1-0 a Livingston.
Aibrox ta yi kokarin samun nasarar farko a waje tun daga nasarar da ta yi a watan Fabrairu da 4-1 a St. Johnstone, amma Gary Holt ta yi nasarar rasa Gerard a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, ta bar kungiyar ta kasa da Harts da maki takwas, wanda ke kan gaba a gasar Ladbrokes.
Menga ya buga minti bakwai kafin rabin wasan kuma raunin da ya yi wa Rangers ya nuna cewa ba zai iya yin nasara ba.
A yanzu da Rangers ta koma matsayi na shida, Livingston ta koma matsayi na uku, da ƙalla kwallo ɗaya daga gaban Hibernian.
Ranger kuma yana da wasu matsaloli da za su iya jawowa, kamar yadda mai kula da aikin, Callum Spence, ya bukaci a yi masa asibiti na farko domin ya ji rauni a kai sakamakon wani abu da aka jefa daga kan bene.
Gerard ya yi canje-canje takwas a cikin tawagar kuma ya sa Ear ta yi rawar jiki a wasan karshe na Betfred Cup.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya yi amfani da wannan rubutun "Livie 11" wanda Hartz ya ba shi digiri a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda wannan injin mai kyau ya iya kashe duk wani ƙoƙarin abokan hamayyarsa.
Ranger ta iya yin nasara a kan mallakar, amma Livingston ta yi nasara a kan ƙwallon.
Ya kamata ya ci a minti na biyu lokacin da Menga ta fara tura Scott Pittman zuwa yankin Alan McGregor, amma matsakaici bai samu kwallon ba.
Wani babban bugun da Keegan Jacobs ya yi ya gano shugaban, Craig Halkett, amma dan wasan sa na gaba, Alan Lithgow, ya iya tura kwallon daga cikin kwando.
'Yan wasan Rangers sun ci gaba da yin nasara, amma a ƙarshen wasan, sun ga cewa za su iya yin nasara.
Alfredo Morelos ya tabbata cewa ya kamata ya yi nasara a 15th, lokacin da ya yi jayayya da Steven Lowles, amma alkalin kotun Steven Thompson ya yi watsi da korafin Kolombiya.
Rangers sun yi harbi biyu a cikin gida a farkon rabin shekara, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Aibrox, Liam Kelly, bai damu da kan Lasana Kuliballi da kuma sautin Obi Ezaria ba.
Ko da yake Livi ya yi kasa da abin da ake tsammani a minti 34 na farko na wasan, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa ya cancanci nasara don ƙoƙarinsa.
Amma, Ranger ta kasa magance matsalar Jacobs.
Scott Orfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da ƙwallon ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe da kwanciyar hankali kuma ya sami Meng'a wanda kawai ya kammala ƙoƙarinsa.
Gerard ya yi canje-canje a cikin rabin lokaci ta hanyar cire Culiballi da kuma sanya Ryan Kent, canjin ya yi tasiri kusan nan da nan, yayin da matsanancin ya wuce kwallon zuwa Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Duk da haka, Livingston ya ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi zuwa salon wasan da ta sani kuma ta ji daɗin, tare da Litgow da Halket suna motsawa daga baya.
Holt zai iya ƙara yawan bambanci zuwa ƙarshen, amma McGregor ya fuskanci Jacobs a kan hanya, yana dakatar da shi kafin Litgo ya yi ƙoƙari daga kusurwar.
A lokacin da ya yi karo da Jacobs, sai Glen Middleton, wani ɗan'uwan da ke aiki a matsayin mataimakin 'yan wasan Rangers, ya yi wani mataki na ƙarshe na cin zarafinsa.
Almanac: Wanda ya kirkiro na'urar auna Geiger
Shafi daga jaridar Sunday Morning: 30 ga Satumba, 1882: kamar yau, shekaru 136 da suka gabata da kuma a yau... ranar da aka haifi mai zuwa mai ilimin lissafi Johann Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanyar ganowa da kuma auna radiation. Wannan binciken ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger gauges.
Tushen kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger mai ƙididdiga ya shiga cikin al'adun gargajiya, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 mai suna Bells of Coronado, wanda ya yi wahayi zuwa ga masana kimiyya masu ban mamaki Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar auna Geiger ce da ake amfani da ita wajen gano abubuwa masu yaduwa kamar su uranium.
Sa'ad da kake saka waɗannan belun kunne, kana jin aikin da mutane suke yi a kan abubuwa na ƙarfe da ke cikin iska".
Evans: "Ka ga, yana yin hauka!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki kadan kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma, wannan ƙwarewar da take ɗauke da sunansa tana ci gaba da aikinta.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa ta koya wa tsarin rigakafi ya "ga" ƙwayoyin da ke da matsala
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa ta koya wa rigakafin jiki ya "ga" ƙwayoyin da ke da matsala kuma ya kashe su
Allurar rigakafi tana koya wa rigakafin ya san ƙwayoyin da ke da matsala a cikin magani
Hanyar ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin mai haƙuri da kuma gyara su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Suna iya ganin furotin da ke cikin cututtukan daji daban-daban kuma su sake yin tashin hankali
Wani rigakafin da ake gwadawa yana da sakamako mai kyau a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da nau'ikan cututtukan daji.
Wata mata da aka yi amfani da allurar rigakafi don ta taimaka wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ya gane ƙwayoyin da ke damunta ta ga kansa na ƙwayoyinta ya ɓace har tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan aikin ya ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga cikin marasa lafiya, gyara su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su "ga" furotin da ake kira HER2, wanda yake da yawa a cikin cututtukan daji, sannan kuma su sake yin amfani da ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzowski, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Abubuwan da aka samu sun nuna cewa muna da wata allurar da za ta kawo bege sosai".
Kamar yadda Farfesa Berzowski ya bayyana, furotin HER2 "yana motsa ciwon daji iri-iri", kamar na nono, na ovarian, na huhu, da na hanji.
An yi amfani da irin wannan tsarin wajen cire ƙwayoyin rigakafi daga marasa lafiya kuma a koya musu yadda za su kai ƙwayoyin daji hari.
Kanye West ya kare Trump, yana saka hular MAGA bayan ya fito a SNL.
Ba ta yi kyau ba
Kanye West ya yi watsi da shi a cikin studio a lokacin wani Saturday Night Live bayan wata hira da aka yi da shi a cikinta ya yaba da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump kuma ya bayyana cewa zai tsaya takara a zaben 2020.
Bayan ya gabatar da waƙarsa ta uku na yamma, mai suna Ghost Town, inda ya sa takalmin baseball tare da taken Make America Great Again, ya ba da misalin rashin amincewa ga 'yan Democrat kuma ya sake goyon bayan Trump.
"Ina yawan magana da wani fararen fata kuma yana cewa, 'To, me ya sa kake son Trump? Yana da wariyar launin fata.'
Idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amirka da daɗewa", in ji ta.
SNL ta fara da wani zane-zane da ya nuna Matt Damon, wanda ya nuna cewa dan wasan Hollywood ya yi amfani da shi wajen gabatar da ikirarin Bret Cavano a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin da Christine Blazey Ford ta yi game da cin zarafin jima'i.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, bidiyon da ke nuna hauka na West ya fito a shafukan sada zumunta na ɗan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock.
Ba a san ko Rock ya yi ƙoƙarin ya yi wa West ba'a da wannan sakon ba.
West ya kuma yi korafi ga jama'a cewa ba a yi masa kyau a bango ba saboda hatinsa.
"Sun yi mini wasan bowling a bango.
Sun ce, "Kada ka fita da hatinka".
Sun yi mini bowling!
Kuma sun ce ban san abin da ke faruwa da ni ba", in ji ta, a cewar Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba da cewa: "Ban san abin da ke faruwa da ni ba? Zan saka rigar Superman, domin idan na yi haka, babu wanda zai iya gaya mini abin da zan yi. Kuna so mutane su ci gaba?
Ku gwada ƙauna".
Aƙalla sau biyu masu sauraro sun ƙi jinin sharhinsa, kuma masu gabatar da shirye-shiryen SNL sun yi kama da suna cikin matsala, in ji Variety, da wani mutum ya ce wa mujallar: "A cikin dukan ɗakin karatu akwai shiru".
