HIV/Aids: China ta ce an samu karuwar 14 cikin 100 na sababbin cututtuka
Kasar Sin ta ce yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
A ƙasar, fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suke fama da cutar, in ji hukumar kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kashi na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kadai, an samu kusan sababbin shari'o'i 40,000.
A yawancin mutane, ana samun sababbin cututtuka ta hanyar jima'i, yana nuna canji daga abin da ya faru a baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin saboda zubar da jini da aka kamu da shi.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya kusan ƙarewa, kamar yadda jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin suka faɗa a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, idan aka kwatanta da shekarar da ta gabata, adadin mutanen da ke rayuwa da HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya ƙaru da kusan 100,000.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i abu ne mai matukar muhimmanci ga al'ummar kasar Sin ta LOAT.
An kawar da cin zarafin 'yan luwadi a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga 'yan kungiyar LGBT ya zama ruwan dare.
Domin ra'ayin da ƙasar take da shi na kiyayewa, an kiyasta cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza za su auri mata a ƙarshe.
Yawancin cututtuka na wannan cuta suna faruwa ne saboda rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun damar yin amfani da magungunan HIV a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance cutar.
Maxin Waters ta musanta cewa wani jami'in ya yi wa 'yan majalisar dokokin Republican leaked bayanai, ta yi tir da "karya mai tsanani" da "kide-kide na hadin kai"
A ranar Asabar, Wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin da ake yi cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar Republican uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yan majalisa 'yan Democrat a Los Angeles sun ce masu sharhi da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na 'yancin-dama ne ke gabatar da wannan ikirarin.
Waters ta wallafa a shafinta na Twitter cewa: "Karyata, ƙarya, da kuma wasu munanan ƙaryace-ƙaryace".
An ce bayanan da aka wallafa sun hada da adiresoshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na Sanatocin Lindsey Graham na Carolina ta Kudu da kuma Mike Lee da Orin Hutch na Utah.
Bayanai sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis kuma wani ba a san shi ba ne ya bayyana su daga yankin Capitol Hill a yayin sauraron kwamitin Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan labarin ya faru ne bayan da 'yan majalisar uku suka yi wa Kavanaw tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu tsaron gida, kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ruwaito cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen rubutun ya danganta da ofishin Waters kuma sun buga bayanan wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, The Hill ta ruwaito.
Waters ta ci gaba da cewa: "Wannan furucin da ba shi da tushe ba ƙarya ce da kuma wauta.
"Wani ma'aikaci na da aka yi wa laifi da ke da shaidar mutum da kuma tsaro saboda waɗannan kalaman na ƙarya da na yaudara ba shi da alhakin wannan bayanin.
Wannan da'awar da ba ta da tushe ba ƙarya ce da kuma wauta ce".
Bayanin Waters ya sami saurin sukar a kan Intanet, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na White House, Ari Flaiser.
"Wannan ƙazanta tana cike da fushi", in ji Flaiser.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da ƙarfin zama mamba a majalisar dokoki.
Idan an zargi wani don abin da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Ba za ta kasance da ƙarfin hali ba.
Bai kamata ya yi tambaya game da abin da ya sa mutumin ya zarge shi ba.
Ya kamata ya kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Flaiser ya kwatanta yadda Waters ta amsa da yadda 'yan Democrat suka yi ba'a ga Alkalin Kavano, wanda masu sukarsa suka zarge shi da cewa ya yi fushi sosai a sauraron ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman tsige Waters a zaben na tsakiya, ya kuma yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Yana da ban mamaki idan gaskiya ne", in ji ta.
A cikin sanarwar, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da "hukumomi masu iko da kuma hukumomin da ke bin doka game da waɗannan kalaman ƙarya".
Ya ci gaba da cewa: "Za mu yi iyakar ƙoƙarinmu mu sa a san waɗanda suka yi laifi kuma mu sa su da alhakin dukan ayyukan da suke da lahani da haɗari ga kowa da kuma dukan ma'aikatanmu".
