Jihohi 18 da kuma yankin Columbia sun goyi bayan tambayar sabon mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma yankin Columbia sun yi ikirarin cewa dokar ta yi tambaya game da sabon manufar Amurka da ta hana ba da mafaka ga wadanda ke neman tsira daga 'yan bindiga ko tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da kuma yankin sun gabatar da rahoton amicus curiae a ranar Juma'a a Washington, D.C., suna goyon bayan mai neman mafaka ya yi tambaya game da wannan manufofin, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a karar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar 'yancin bil'adama ta Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta ba.
Ta ce mijinta "da 'ya'yansa maza masu zalunci da suke cikin 'yan bindiga" suna wulakanta ta, duk da haka, jami'an Amurka sun ƙi takardar ta ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare shi a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, inda yawancin masu neman mafaka suka fito daga Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar matsaloli masu tsanani na 'yan bindiga da tashin hankali a cikin gida.
Sabon manufar baƙi ta Amurka ta juya hukuncin 2014 da Hukumar Kula da Baƙi ta Yi (BIA) ya yanke kuma ya ba da damar baƙi marasa izini waɗanda ke tserewa daga yanayin tashin hankali na gida don neman mafaka.
A ranar Juma'a, Babban Lauyan Kotun District of Columbia, Karl Rassin, ya ce sabon manufar "ta yi watsi da shekaru da yawa na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya".
"A karkashin dokar tarayya, dole ne a yi la'akari da duk bukatar mafaka bisa ga abubuwan da suka faru da kuma yanayin da ake bukata. Irin wannan ƙuntatawa ya keta wannan ka'ida", in ji amicus curiae.
Lauyoyin sun kuma yi ikirarin cewa dokar hana shiga ga 'yan gudun hijira tana cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna da'awar cewa sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su "zama ma'aikata masu mahimmanci".
A watan Yuni, Babban Shari'a Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan da ke kula da batun ƙaura su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke ƙoƙarin tserewa daga yanayin tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma 'yan bindiga.
"An ba da mafaka ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko kuma barazana saboda launin fata, addini, ƙasa ko kasancewa cikin wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar da ya yi a ranar 11 ga Yuni game da siyasa.
Ba a taɓa yin tanadin mafaka don magance dukan matsalolin (har ma da na musamman) da mutane suke fuskanta a yau da kullum a duniya ba.
