Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet don ya yi gwagwarmaya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya fara wani kamfani da ke neman ya yi gasa da Facebook da Amazon da kuma Google.
Sabuwar ciwon da aka samu a wannan almara ta fasaha ita ce Inrupt, wani kamfani da ke dogara ne akan dandamali na Solids na Berners Lee.
Aikin dandalin Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su, da kuma wanda za su iya samun dama da kuma wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi hakan yanzu", in ji shi game da kamfanin.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar dandamali na Solid ta ba masu amfani damar ƙirƙirar nasu "sashin ajiyar bayanan sirri" ko POD.
Yana iya ɗauke da jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyukan da ke jiran aiki, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin wani browser kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abu na musamman da ke tattare da wurin ajiye bayanai na sirri na yanar gizo shi ne cewa yana ba mai amfani damar yanke shawara ko wane ne ke samun dama ga wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar babban jami'in kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce ta samar da albarkatu, hanyoyin da kuma basira don sanya dandamali na Solid a kan kowa.
Kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu tsara shirye-shiryen da suka yi aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere kere a duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da suka mallaka ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke shafin Inrupt.
Berners Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za a ba su damar yin canje-canje masu zurfi, suna rushe tsarin kasuwanci a cikin dare.
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A wani rubutu a Medium da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai kare mutuncin da kuma ingancin sabon kayan da aka samar bisa dandalin Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar World Wide Web a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts (MIT).
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Har ma da Inrupt, Berners Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya kasance darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da bege sosai game da zamanin da za a yi amfani da intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
