Wani sabon jinkiri ga sabon jirgin saman Jamus
A cewar kafofin watsa labarai na yankin, an sa sabon jirgin ruwan na rundunar sojan ruwa na Jamus a cikin shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na zamanin Cold War, amma ba za a karɓi shi ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa aƙalla saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar da ake samu.
An dage aikin jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz, wanda shi ne babban jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg, har zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, in ji jaridar Die Zeit, inda wani wakilin rundunar sojin kasar ya yi magana.
Ya kamata a shigar da jirgin cikin Navy a 2014, amma matsalolin bayarwa sun kasance mahimmanci ga nasarar wannan shirin mai ban sha'awa.
Jirgin ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da aka ba da umarni daga Rundunar Sojan Ruwa a 2007 za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Za su kawo makamai masu ƙarfi, wasu makamai masu linzami da kuma makamai masu linzami, da wasu fasahohin ɓoye kamar rage radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Sauran manyan abubuwan da ke faruwa su ne rage yawan aikin kulawa, saboda zai yiwu a yi amfani da sabbin jiragen ruwa har tsawon shekaru biyu a waje da tashoshin jiragen ruwa na Jamus.
Duk da haka, jinkirin da ake yi a nan gaba yana nufin cewa, ko da yake ana ganin jiragen ruwa na soja na zamani ne, wanda zai ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje, har sai da aka shigar da su, za su riga sun tsufa, in ji Die Zeit.
F-125 ya zama sananne a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi karɓar jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi a cikin tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojin ruwa ta koma wani jirgi bayan an kai shi.
Ba a san cikakken bayani game da dalilan dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ruwaito wasu manyan "rashin amfani da software da kayan aiki" da za su sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani idan aka yi amfani da shi a aikin yaƙi.
Matsalolin software sun kasance da muhimmanci sosai, tun da yake jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg suna da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa kimanin 120, kusan rabinsa idan aka kwatanta da tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma bayyana cewa jirgin yana da nauyi mai yawa, wanda ke rage yawan aiki kuma yana iyakance ikon Navy don ƙara haɓaka a nan gaba.
An yi imani cewa jirgin ruwan Rheinland-Pfalz mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jiragen ruwa na irin wannan rukunin da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin aikin duka (ciki har da horar da ma'aikatan) kuma batun ne.
An ce an kai adadin da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin harshen Turanci na Euro 3.1 biliyan (Euro 3,6 biliyan), yayin da kasafin kudin farko ya kai Euro 2.2 biliyan.
Matsalar da ke damun sababbin jiragen ruwa na musamman ce a yayin da sojojin ruwa na Jamus ke raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekara, Hans Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa Rundunar Sojan Ruwa "ba za ta daɗe ba ba za ta sami jiragen ruwa don yin aiki".
Jami'in ya ce matsalar ta ƙaru a tsawon lokaci domin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa sun lalace amma babu wasu jiragen ruwa da za su maye gurbin su.
Ya yi ikirarin cewa babu wani jirgin ruwan Baden-Wuerttemberg da ya shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa.
Ƙungiyar Ƙasa ta Kasa tana ɓoye rayuwar ɓoye na bats
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a wani gonar da ke cikin Highlands na Scotland ya nuna yadda tsuntsaye suke amfani da shimfidar wuri don neman abinci.
Wannan binciken zai kawo sabon haske game da halayyar waɗannan tsuntsaye masu tashi da kuma taimaka wajen tsara ayyukan kare muhalli na gaba.
Binciken da masana kimiyya na National Trust suka yi na Scotland zai bincika halaye na nanobatter da microbeater, da kuma brown otonobater da Dobbendan myodite a Inverewe Gardens, a Wester Ross.
