Shugaban kungiyar Sunderland Jack Ross ya ce "babbar burinsa" shi ne ya zama kocin tawagar Scotland.
Dan wasan mai shekara 42 mai suna Scotch yana farin ciki da za a yi masa kwallo don ya sake gina tawagar arewa maso gabashin Ingila, wadda a yanzu tana matsayi na uku a gasar Premier ta Ingila (League One), maki uku a kasa da ta.
