Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afku a tsibirin Sulawesi a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai girma 7.5 ta Richter ta jawo tsunami kuma ta lalata dubban gidaje.
An katse wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afku kusa da babban birnin Sulawesi, wanda ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
A shafukan sada zumunta, ana samun bidiyo na abin da ya faru.
Dubban mutane sun taru don bikin a bakin teku a garin Paulo lokacin da tsunami ya afku a bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa mai wuya ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York suna neman a yi wa Saiful Saiyopov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a saba yi a jihar ba saboda aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saiyopov, mai shekaru 30, an ce ya yi amfani da wata motar hayar gida ta Home Depot don kai hari kan titin keke a kan titin West Side a Lower Manhattan, yana garzaya da matafiya da kuma masu hawa keke da aka samu a titin a ranar 31 ga Oktoba.
Don a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Saiyopov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma ya yi wa mutane lahani "da gangan", a cewar wata sanarwa da aka gabatar a Kotun Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan zargin sun kai ga hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar.
Makonni bayan harin, wani kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saiyopov da laifin da ake zargi da shi na 22 wanda ya hada da zargin kisa na mutum takwas da ake zargi da aikata laifi, wata dabara da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da ita a lokuta na aikata laifi, da kuma laifin yin amfani da karfi da lalata motocin mota.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma shiri", suna bayyana yadda Saiyopov ya kai harin a matsayin "mai ban tsoro, mai tsanani da kuma rashin amfani".
"Saifulo Habibullayevich Saiyopov ya jawo wa iyalan da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Clives, An-Lor Decad, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlich, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Panuko azaba, da lahani da asarar", kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin sanarwar niyyar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ta shige tun lokacin da kotun Kudancin New York ta yi shari'a game da wani abu da ya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Halid Barnes, hukuncin kisa a kan 'yan kasuwa biyu, amma a ƙarshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai a watan Satumba na 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke wa mijinta Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a New York don yin rahoto a kan gwamnatin Soviet a lokacin yakin sanyi.
An kashe su a cikin kujera a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saiyopov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, ya bayyana ba tare da yin nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni da suka biyo bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa ya gamsu da aikinsa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saiyopov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa bidiyon ISIS ne ya hure shi ya kai harin, kamar yadda ake cewa a wayar sa.
Ya kuma nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan zargin 22 da aka yi masa.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin masu gabatar da kara na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saiyopov, ya ce sun "bayyana cewa sun yi takaici" da hukuncin da hukumar ta yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawara da za a nemi a yi kisa maimakon a yi masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar a sake shi ba zai ƙara wa dukan waɗanda suka yi laifi raunin da ya faru", in ji Patton.
