Syria ta "shirya" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, a cewar Ministan Harkokin Wajen
Syria ta ce ta shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira da son rai kuma ta nemi taimako wajen sake gina kasar da yaki ya shafe shekaru bakwai (da kuma yanzu).
Da yake jawabi a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen kasar, Walid al-Mu'aleem, ya ce yanayin ƙasar yana inganta.
"Yanzu, halin da ake ciki a ƙasar ya fi kwanciyar hankali da kwanciyar hankali saboda ci gaba da aka samu a yaƙi da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnatin ta ci gaba da mayar da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'ada.
Yanzu an cika dukkan sharudda don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira da aka tilasta musu su bar kasar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na yau da kullum da suka shafi rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar ƙasar tun lokacin da yaƙin ya barke a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al Mu'aleem ya ce gwamnatin Syria ta yi maraba da taimakon da ake bayarwa don sake gina ƙasar da ta rushe.
Sai dai ya ce ba zai karbi tallafi ko taimako daga kasashen da suka goyi bayan tawayen ba.
Turai ta kammala cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup 2018, ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka ta ƙarshe da maki 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin golf na Le Golf National, a waje da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu dai, an ci nasarar buga gasar cin kofin Ryder a Turai sau shida a jere, kuma an lashe gasar a Turai tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun matsayi na farko, kamar yadda tawagar shugaban Denmark Thomas Björn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don ta doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelston, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya sosai a tsawon lokacin gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a ramin par-3 na 16, ya ba da nasara ga Francisco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Mollinari ya yi nasara a duk zagaye, kuma ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka yi nasara 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a yau, a 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spith ya ci nasara a 5&4 a hannun Danno Thorbjørn Olsen, dan wasan da ya fi kasa a gasar Turai.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ya fi kowacce daraja a duniya, ya ci 2 da 1 a kan Ian Pultner na Ingila, wanda zai iya buga wasansa na karshe a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Tsohon dan wasan Spain mai cin kofin Ryder na takwas, Sergio Garcia ya zama dan Turai mafi nasara a gasar a duk lokacin da ya zira kwallaye 25.5.
