A lokacin da aka yi wa 'yan wasan kwallon kafa na Turai gasar, ya ce: "Na yi farin ciki cewa na taimaka.
Ya ba da gudummawa ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram, wanda ya ci wasan golf na Tiger Woods 2&1 a wasan mutum a ranar Lahadi.
"Ina alfahari da cewa na yi nasara a kan Tiger Woods, na girma ina sha'awar wannan mutumin", in ji Ram mai shekara 23.
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin wasan Raider Cup 13-21-3.
Wannan baƙon ƙididdiga ba ne ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na kowane lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan lakabi 14 kuma Jack Nicklaus ne kawai ya fi shi.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi ta fama da matsala a ƙarshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Fino, waɗanda suka buga golf na gaba a gasar.
